{
  "text": "The mechanism of toxic action of abrin is identical to that of ricin, but the toxicity of abrin in mice is 75 times higher that of ricin (0.04 \u00b5g/kg for abrin compared to 3 \u00b5g/kg for ricin). The diagnosis, clinical features, treatment, protection, prophylaxis and so on is also the same for both abrin and ricin intoxications [CITATION_1] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
